##---------------------------------------------------------------------
@node SUPPORT "Support"

                   @{b}>> Support <<@{ub}

 I have created a mailing list for AmiGate.

 This list will replace the AmiGate new version server and of course also
allow for discussion and questions of gating issues.

 To subscribe send an email to <listserv@boble.ping.dk> with bodytext

ADD amigatelist

 After that you should receive a message confirming that you have been
added together with a short introduction to the list. (The listserver also
understands several other commands, send email with bodytext HELP to
receive a list of supported commands).

 To submit mailings to the list, send your emails to the address
<amigatelist@boble.ping.dk>.

 If you want the mailinglist to be gated into a FidoNet area you can place
the following line in your AmiGate.areas (replace youruserid with your own
userid).

MAILLIST + AMIGATELIST <youruserid> amigatelist@boble.ping.dk
@endnode

